[2026-06-13] [5_Symbols] [HIGH] — 404 Not Found for /api/images/enhance-prompt after implementation. Endpoint likely not active in running server.
[2026-06-13] 🔴 [5_Symbols/image_generator.html] [HIGH] — Gemini "Enhance" and "Generate" buttons fail silently. Root cause: (1) Go server does not load `.env` file — `os.Getenv("GEMINI_API_KEY")` returns empty when run outside sourcing; (2) Model `gemini-1.5-flash` not available — only `gemini-2.5-flash` and newer are available for this key. Fix: added `loadDotEnv(".env")` in `loadConfig()`, added `/api/images/test-gemini` endpoint, added test-connection button on the page, changed all `gemini-1.5-flash` → `gemini-2.5-flash`.
[2026-06-13] 🔴 [5_Symbols/image_generator.html] [HIGH] — Azure save "azure upload failed". Root cause: `Transfer-Encoding: chunked` not supported by Azure Blob Storage PUT requests when body is streamed directly from HTTP response. Fix: read body into buffer, use `bytes.NewReader()`, set explicit `Content-Length` header.
[2026-06-13] 🐛 [5_Symbols] [HIGH] — Image generator returned a hardcoded Unsplash placeholder instead of generating with Gemini; output looked low-quality/unrelated to the prompt vs. the Gemini web app.
